{"tid":2078491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［求幫推］黑警性暴力受害人們拍咗條英文片，勞煩大家幫手CLS","createTime":"2020-06-25T05:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T03:49:46.000Z","uid":233174,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"954abb749ed9ccbcd66d97fc89251a7f7cd4fe9e","tid":2078491,"uid":233174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋一班受黑警性暴力嘅受害人<br />\n選擇咗再一次企出嚟發聲</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前開記招嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>少女K</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">多次被黑警揸胸、進行第三級別裸搜、女警哄近佢下體、如廁時被在旁觀看、患PTSD多次自殺未遂<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>男生C</strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">被女警裸搜虐打下體</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">性暴力受害人係無分男女</span></strong></span><br />\n男女都會受傷，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>任何人都有保障自己不被性暴力傷害嘅權利</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有開記招指控被裸搜嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>呂小姐、Sonia吳傲雪、8月5天水圍少女</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋拍咗一條片<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我哋忍痛重提自己經歷<br />\n希望可以再次引起國際關注</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SQ3-OZaEcCA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSQ3-OZaEcCA&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=aec34178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SQ3-OZaEcCA</a><br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】受害人挺身拍片向國際作證港警性暴力<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZjLZ59\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZjLZ59&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=d9f61679\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZjLZ59</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>對受害人有咩冷嘲熱諷嘅，勞煩高抬貴手啦</ins></span></strong><br />\nWords can kill.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋願意出嚟發聲，我哋唔知嚟緊有咩成果<br />\n只係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>憑良知不顧一切盡做</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WtOPWCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtOPWCD.jpg&h=467c58d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>寧可最後徒勞無功，<br />\n也不選擇無動於衷。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1c18e4610f40fa82f892cafe85f817d463735f37","tid":2078491,"uid":233174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5202fc4fb72362fc03a99274e5479fcda57832be","tid":2078491,"uid":233174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a2298ebe0576adaa79badcab611b1551cbac62","tid":2078491,"uid":233174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:47:50.000Z","msg":"自推9連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b8a667a81a90e8d868b8d6ab605cd466199bfb","tid":2078491,"uid":233174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"自推8連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1460571f4cfe253b2d73bb556514c9bde028bea4","tid":2078491,"uid":233174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:48:31.000Z","msg":"自推7連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2552f384ba0ccd9c4eae3e8f6a48a8d